com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport

Class EntityPlaceholder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.CoreItem
      • com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.ItemPlaceholder
        • com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.EntityPlaceholder

  • public final class EntityPlaceholder
extends ItemPlaceholder
    A placeholder for an Entity that contains less information. An EntityPlaceholder is used in place of an Entity when:
    • the Entity has been deleted, or
    • the Entity has been purged, or
    • the current user has only the SecurityAccessLevel.READ_CLOAKED access level on the Entity, or
    • the current user has the SecurityAccessLevel.NONE access level and the SecurityGrantLevel.UPDATE grant level on the Entity
    Since:
    1.0
